            "heading": "Patchouli & Cedarwood",
            "detail": "Earthy Cedarwood with wafts of woody-citrus MayChang and Patchouli, followed by floral Palmarosa and sweet-balsamic Amyris. These star alongside natural insecticide Neem for moth-free wardrobes!",
            "pop_heading": "Patchouli & Cedarwood",
            "pop_detail": "Top Notes  MayChang - an intense fresh and citrusy aroma with insecticidal and calming properties.   Middle Notes  Palmarosa - a sweet, floral-rosy oil that’s antimicrobial and acts as an insect repellent.    Base Notes  Red Cedarwood - a woody aroma with sweet balsamic scent that helps deter moths.  Patchouli - a rich, sweet, herbaceous and aromatic aroma traditionally used as a moth and insect repellent.",
            "showplus": true,
            "PoopupIconCode": "<div>\n            <img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0360/1347/3931/files/Amyris.png?v=1678290093\">\n        </div>\n<div>\n\n  <img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0360/1347/3931/files/maychang.png?v=1678290093\">\n        </div>\n<div>\n\n  <img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0360/1347/3931/files/cedarwood.png?v=1678290096\">\n        </div>\n<div>\n\n  <img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0360/1347/3931/files/patchouli.png?v=1678290096\">\n        </div>\n<div>\n\n  <img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0360/1347/3931/files/poalmarosa.png?v=1678290097\">\n        </div>\n<div>\n</div>"
          }
        },
        "60dfab80-c376-4794-a2a6-9eb787e14034": {
